divs: Sighting DetailsTaking pictures of the trails in the cloud. I did t notice it until I looked at the images I shot. I didn't know what it was, just that I knew what it wasn't. I saw no motion, it was gone ing the time my next image was shot. I was a little unnerved and uncomfortable. It disappeared.
Summary: Taking random images of the sky and caught this is one photo. I was looking at strange trails in the clouds as if something was swiping through, leaving noticeable trails in otherwise fluffy clouds in a blue sky.
